headline: BMO Capital Reiterates ‘Outperform’ Rating on Fair Isaac Corp (FICO), Cuts Price Target
summary: Fair Isaac Corporation (NYSE:FICO) is one of the best depressed stocks to buy in 2025. On August 4, BMO Capital reiterated its ‘Outperform’ rating on the stock but reduced the price target to $1,650 from $1,800. The price target adjustment follows an expert event by Clayton Dukes, a former senior employee, on August 1. The […]
